    <item>
      <title>美联储官员保留 12 月利率决策选项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/fed-s-waller-says-he-s-leaning-toward-rate-cut-in-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三位美联储官员周一明确表示，他们预计美联储将在未来一年继续降息，但没有表示他们承诺在本月晚些时候进行下一次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/fed-s-waller-says-he-s-leaning-toward-rate-cut-in-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 20:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃莱克特拉股价暴跌，萨利纳斯一天损失 55 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/salinas-set-to-lose-4-billion-in-a-day-as-elektra-slumps-60</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在停牌数月后，周一恢复交易的 Grupo Elektra 股价暴跌 71%，亿万富翁里卡多·萨利纳斯·普利戈 (Ricardo Salinas Pliego) 的财富因此蒸发 55 亿美元，并使其跌出世界 500 大富豪榜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/salinas-set-to-lose-4-billion-in-a-day-as-elektra-slumps-60</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 15:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
